snippet.title: Codename: GOD - Trailer
snippet.description:
Somewhere in the 80s, lives Randall, a nerdy kid who hopes to win the heart of the most popular girl in school. He meets you, a divine entity who will guide him on this journey.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2962840/Codename_GOD/

Trailer music is Born A Tiger by John Bartmann (from Free Music Archive)
